org.spongepowered.api.data.key

Interface Key<V extends BaseValue<?>>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - The type of BaseValue
    All Superinterfaces:
    CatalogType

    @CatalogedBy(value=Keys.class)
public interface Key<V extends BaseValue<?>>
extends CatalogType
    Represents a key to an underlying BaseValue such that the underlying value can be retrieved from a ValueContainer. As well, a Key can be used for DataSerializables with the included getQuery() to retrieve the recommended DataQuery to use.
